HEY. YOU COMING TO CORY'S

00:22.021 --> 00:23.691
BIRTHDAY PARTY THIS WEEKEND?

00:23.732 --> 00:26.360
-[ Laughing ] OF COURSE.

00:23.732 --> 00:26.360
WHAT IS HE, LIKE 13?

00:23.732 --> 00:26.360
-14.

00:26.401 --> 00:27.778
CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

00:27.820 --> 00:28.863
WELL, WE'RE GETTING OLD.

00:28.904 --> 00:30.071
[ Laughing ] YEAH.

00:30.113 --> 00:31.782
HEY, YOU WANT LISA TO MAKE

00:30.113 --> 00:31.782
HER POTATO SALAD?

00:31.824 --> 00:33.325
ONLY REASON

00:31.824 --> 00:33.325
YOU WERE INVITED, BOY.

00:33.367 --> 00:35.577
I'M NOT PAYING YOU BOYS

00:33.367 --> 00:35.577
TO LOLLYGAG!

